          <li>Adhere to industry safety standards and best practices</li>
          <li>Provide accurate information regarding well conditions and site hazards</li>
          <li>Maintain appropriate insurance coverage</li>
          <li>Follow Wood Wireline's safety protocols and procedures</li>
